aradigm InfoTech, he worked with IBM and Satyam Computers. He holds a degree in Master’s of Science in Computers and is a graduate from the Harvard Business School. He is an active member of Young Presidents Organisation, a Charter Member of TiE Hyderabad and is on the governing council of AP Society for Knowledge Networks and also on the academic council of Vignan University.\r\n<div class=\"content-text-1\">Karthik Krishnan: Chief Financial Officer &amp; CEO – eCentricHR:</div>\r\nKarthik brings with him 14 years of experience of working with large corporate houses in Business strategy, corporate finance and Business Intelligence. Prior to Paradigm, he worked in leadership roles with A F Ferguson &amp; Co. (Deloitte), Chartered Accountants, Arvind Mills, Maini Precision Components and NSL Group. He is a qualified Chartered Accountant with proven track record in managing large scale enterprises.\r\n<div class=\"content-text-1\">Arindam Chakraborthy: Senior Vice President – IT Staffing</div>\r\nArindam is an IT veteran with 26  years of experience and was instrumental  in essaying roles in Business & Change Management, Delivery & Sales Operations and P&L Management Pan India for different organizations. He joins us from Technosoft Global Corp. where he was responsible for setting up the business from the inception stage and scaling it to a world class Managed and Consulting Services Centre. Prior to this he has held various key leadership positions at Magna InfoTech, Ingram Micro, InfoTech Enterprises and other prominent enterprises. An MBA from Salt Lake Institute of Technical Training in Calcutta University, with Graduation in Commerce from St. Xavier’s College, Arindam is a certified Sales Specialist from HP/Compaq.\r\n<div class=\"content-text-1\">Siva Prasad Nanduri: Head of IT Staffing:</div>\r\nSiva brings to eCentric an experience of 17 years in sales, staff augmentation and staffing. Prior to eCentric Siva has served with TEK Systems, Adecco, Tata Teleservices TBA and GE iGate Capital. He is a qualified management graduate(Executive Program) from IIM Kolkata and a qualified six sigma practioner.\r\n<div class=\"content-text-1\">Rob Studer: President</div>\r\nRob brings over 20 years of work experience. Rob has extensive experience in Wireless, Mobile Apps, Security and ERP. Strong customer relationships and rapid revenue growth under his leadership has been the driving force behind acquisitions of companies. Rob has also done business with companies such as Comcast, Time Warner, CableVision, Sprint and BrightHouse Networks. Rob is a graduate of the Iowa State University School of Business.\r\n<div class=\"content-text-1\">Chrishtopher Ponsford: Vice President</div>\r\nChris has over 17 years of experience in rail transportation, medical, electronics and aerospace. He has designed and implemented Quality Standards procedures interfacing directly with customers and development teams globally creating successful profitable solutions for fortune 500 companies globally. By understanding their needs, Chris creates innovative solutions to fit customers goals and budgets.</div>\r\n[contact_form]\r\n</div>\r\n','Leadership','','publish','open','open','','leadership','','','2015-03-31 11:06:08','2015-03-31 11:06:08','',18,'http://103.230.84.14/?page_id=153',4,'page','',0),(154,1,'2014-05-13 15:05:14','2014-05-13 15:05:14','<div class=\"content-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"content-main\">\r\n<div class=\"banner-nner\"><a href=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/general2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-123\" src=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/general2.jpg\" alt=\"general\" width=\"980\" height=\"200\" /></a></div>\r\n<div id=\"breadcrumbMenu\">\r\n<div class=\"breadcrumb\"><a href=\"http://localhost/ecen/\">Home</a><a href=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/arrow.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-20\" src=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/