l wp-image-20\" src=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/arrow.png\" alt=\"arrow\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" /></a> <a href=\"http://103.230.84.14/about-us/\">About Us</a><a href=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/arrow.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-20\" src=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/arrow.png\" alt=\"arrow\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" /></a><a href=\"http://103.230.84.14/about-us/company-overview/\">Company Overview</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"body-block\">\r\n<div class=\"contentt-block\">\r\n<div class=\"header-text-1\">Company Overview</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h1 class=\"content-text-1\">eCENTRIC</h1>\r\neCentric is Indian arm of the US$100 Million ParadigmIT Group. Established in 2002 as an RPO and offshore venture of ParadigmIT US, eCentric has subsequently built expertise in enterprise IT solutions and end to end human resource solutions.\r\n\r\neCentric is a CMMi Level 3, ISO 9001, ISO 27001 certified company with proven delivery capabilities in software development, support services, Recruitment Process Outsourcing, Business Process Outsourcing and end-to-end human resource solutions. We currently work with Fortune 500 companies and organizations from Government of India, US Government and large and medium Indian corporates.\r\n<h1 class=\"content-text-1\">eCentricHR</h1>\r\nWith over 16 years of experience in this field eCentricHR is the human resource solutions business of the company and focusses on providing search, selection, staffing, staff augmentation and training in India and USA. At eCentric we believe in providing customers with efficient and <b class=\"testimonials\">effective human resource solutions</b> on back of proprietary delivery process and mechanism.\r\n\r\nOur focus on offering efficient and timely solutions to customer has allowed us to deploy over 2500 resources across India in short span of last 3 years. We continue to deliver top tier talent across industry verticals and solutions with dedicated team based out of all major Indian cities and USA.\r\n\r\neCentricHR is member of industry bodies such as Indian Staffing Federation (ISF) , Associated Chambers of Commerce and Industry of India (ASSOCHAM), National Association of Software and Services Companies (NASSCOM) and TiE.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"ourvalue1-1\">\r\n<ul class=\"responsive-accordion responsive-accordion-default bm-larger\">\r\n	<li>\r\n<div class=\"responsive-accordion-head\">Contact Us<i class=\"fa fa-chevron-down responsive-accordion-plus fa-fw\"></i><i class=\"fa fa-chevron-up responsive-accordion-minus fa-fw\" style=\"display: none;\"></i></div>\r\n<div class=\"responsive-accordion-panel\">\r\n\r\n[contact-form-7 id=\"409\" title=\"contct inner page\"]\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Company Overview','','inherit','open','open','','116-revision-v1','','','2014-05-13 15:39:28','2014-05-13 15:39:28','',116,'http://103.230.84.14/116-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(190,1,'2014-05-13 15:41:25','2014-05-13 15:41:25','<div class=\"content-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"content-main\">\r\n<div class=\"banner-nner\"><a href=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/culture.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-46\" src=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/culture.jpg\" alt=\"culture\" width=\"980\" height=\"200\" /></a></div>\r\n<div id=\"breadcrumbMenu\">\r\n<div class=\"breadcrumb\"><a href=\"http://localhost/ecen/\">Home</a><a href=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/arrow.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-20\" src=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/arrow.png\" alt=\"arrow\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" /></a><a href=\"http://localhost/ecen/careers/\">Careers</a><a href=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/arrow.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-20\" src=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/arr