/103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/arrow2.jpg\" alt=\"arrow2\" width=\"20\" height=\"6\" /></a>In depth understanding of developing application on the Force.com platform\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/arrow2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-22\" src=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/arrow2.jpg\" alt=\"arrow2\" width=\"20\" height=\"6\" /></a>In depth knowledge of REST/SOAP APIs and building integration with Salesforce\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/arrow2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-22\" src=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/arrow2.jpg\" alt=\"arrow2\" width=\"20\" height=\"6\" /></a>Good working knowledge of HTML, CSS, javascript, jQuery, JSON\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/arrow2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-22\" src=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/arrow2.jpg\" alt=\"arrow2\" width=\"20\" height=\"6\" /></a>Excellent analysis and problem solving abilities\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/arrow2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-22\" src=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/arrow2.jpg\" alt=\"arrow2\" width=\"20\" height=\"6\" /></a>Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science or related field\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"ourvalue1-1\">\r\n<ul class=\"responsive-accordion responsive-accordion-default bm-larger\">\r\n	<li>\r\n<div class=\"responsive-accordion-head\">Share your details:<i class=\"fa fa-chevron-down responsive-accordion-plus fa-fw\"></i><i class=\"fa fa-chevron-up responsive-accordion-minus fa-fw\" style=\"display: none;\"></i></div>\r\n<div class=\"responsive-accordion-panel\">\r\n\r\n[contact-form-7 id=\"405\" title=\"Contact form contct us page\"]\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Salesforce developer Job Description','','inherit','open',