 />\r\n<h1 class=\"content-text-1\">eCentricHR</h1>\r\nWith over 16 years of experience in this field eCentricHR is the human resource solutions business of the company and focusses on providing search, selection, staffing, staff augmentation and training in India and USA. At eCentric we believe in providing customers with efficient and <b class=\"testimonials\">effective human resource solutions</b> on back of proprietary delivery process and mechanism.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOur focus on offering efficient and timely solutions to customer has allowed us to deploy over 2500 resources across India in short span of last 3 years. We continue to deliver top tier talent across industry verticals and solutions with dedicated team based out of all major Indian cities and USA.<br />\r\n<br />\r\neCentricHR is member of industry bodies such as Indian Staffing Federation (ISF) , Associated Chambers of Commerce and Industry of India (ASSOCHAM),  National Association of Software and Services Companies (NASSCOM) and TiE.\r\n</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n[contact_form]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Company Overview','','inherit','open','open','','116-revision-v1','','','2014-05-16 07:04:21','2014-05-16 07:04:21','',116,'http://103.230.84.14/116-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(437,1,'2014-05-16 07:05:27','2014-05-16 07:05:27','<div class=\"content-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"content-main\">\r\n<div class=\"banner-nner\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-42 size-full\" src=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/careers-header.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"980\" height=\"200\" /></div>\r\n<div id=\"breadcrumbMenu\">\r\n<div class=\"breadcrumb\"><a href=\"http://103.230.84.14/\">Home</a><a href=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/arrow.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-20\" src=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/arrow.png\" alt=\"arrow\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" /></a> <a href=\"http://103.230.84.14/about-us/\">About Us</a><a href=\"http://103.2