\" alt=\"arrow\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" /></a>Leadership</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"body-block\">\r\n<div class=\"contentt-block\">\r\n<p>\r\n<div class=\"header-text-1\">Leadership</div>\r\n<div class=\"content-text-1\">Sridhar Gadhi: Founder and Group CEO</div>\r\nSridhar is a first generation entrepreneur. He started Paradigm InfoTech in 1998, eCentric Solutions in 2002 and has been growing the group ever since. He is a dynamic leader and built companies by developing leaders and successful teams. He has abilities to build companies in various industries that have huge growth prospects and steer them to success. Sridhar was awarded Entrepreneur of the year award by Ernst &amp;Young and Young Entrepreneurs Award by TANA.\r\nPrior to starting Paradigm InfoTech, he worked with IBM and Satyam Computers. He holds a degree in Master’s of Science in Computers and is a graduate from the Harvard Business School.\r\nHe is an active member of Young Presidents Organisation, a Charter Member of TiE Hyderabad and is on the governing council of AP Society for Knowledge Networks and also on the academic council of Vignan University.\r\n<div class=\"content-text-1\">Karthik Krishnan: Chief Financial Officer &amp; CEO – eCentricHR:</div>\r\nKarthik brings with him 14 years of experience of working with large corporate houses in Business strategy, corporate finance and Business Intelligence. Prior to Paradigm, he worked in leadership roles with A F Ferguson &amp; Co. (Deloitte), Chartered Accountants, Arvind Mills, Maini Precision Components and NSL Group. He is a qualified Chartered Accountant with proven track record in managing large scale enterprises.\r\n<div class=\"content-text-1\">Siva Prasad Nanduri: Head of IT Staffing:</div>\r\nSiva brings to eCentric an experience of 17 years in sales, staff augmentation and staffing. Prior to eCentric Siva has served with TEK Systems, Adecco, Tata Teleservices TBA and GE iGate Capital. He is a qualified management graduate from IIM Kolkata and a qualified six sigma practioner.\r\n<div class=\"content-text-1\">Rob Studer: President</div>\r\nRob brings over 20 years of work experience. Rob has extensive experience in Wireless, Mobile Apps, Security and ERP. Strong customer relationships and rapid revenue growth under his leadership has been the driving force behind acquisitions of companies. Rob has also done business with companies such as Comcast, Time Warner, CableVision, Sprint and BrightHouse Networks. Rob is a graduate of the Iowa State University School of Business.\r\n<div class=\"content-text-1\">Chrishtopher Ponsford: Vice President</div>\r\nChris has over 17 years of experience in rail transportation, medical, electronics and aerospace. He has designed and implemented Quality Standards procedures interfacing directly with customers and development teams globally creating successful profitable solutions for fortune 500 companies globally. By understanding their needs, Chris creates innovative solutions to fit customers goals and budgets.\r\n</p>\r\n</div>\r\n[contact_form]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Leadership','','inherit','open','open','','153-revision-v1','','','2014-05-16 07:06:07','2014-05-16 07:06:07','',153,'http://103.230.84.14/153-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(439,1,'2014-05-16 07:06:29','2014-05-16 07:06:29','<div class=\"content-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"content-main\">\r\n<div class=\"banner-nner\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-42\" src=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/careers-header.jpg\" alt=\"careers-header\" width=\"980\" height=\"200\" /></div>\r\n<div id=\"breadcrumbMenu\">\r\n<div class=\"breadcrumb\"><a href=\"http://103.230.84.14/\">Home</a><a href=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/arrow.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-20\" src=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/arrow.png\" alt=\"arrow\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" /></a> <a href=\"http://103.230.84.14/about-us/\">About Us</a>