ce of 17 years in sales, staff augmentation and staffing. Prior to eCentric Siva has served with TEK Systems, Adecco, Tata Teleservices TBA and GE iGate Capital. He is a qualified management graduate from IIM Kolkata and a qualified six sigma practioner.\r\n<div class=\"content-text-1\">Rob Studer: President</div>\r\nRob brings over 20 years of work experience. Rob has extensive experience in Wireless, Mobile Apps, Security and ERP. Strong customer relationships and rapid revenue growth under his leadership has been the driving force behind acquisitions of companies. Rob has also done business with companies such as Comcast, Time Warner, CableVision, Sprint and BrightHouse Networks. Rob is a graduate of the Iowa State University School of Business.\r\n<div class=\"content-text-1\">Chrishtopher Ponsford: Vice President</div>\r\nChris has over 17 years of experience in rail transportation, medical, electronics and aerospace. He has designed and implemented Quality Standards procedures interfacing directly with customers and development teams globally creating successful profitable solutions for fortune 500 companies globally. By understanding their needs, Chris creates innovative solutions to fit customers goals and budgets.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[contact_form]\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Leadership','','inherit','open','open','','153-revision-v1','','','2014-05-21 07:52:16','2014-05-21 07:52:16','',153,'http://103.230.84.14/153-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(538,1,'2014-05-21 07:53:10','2014-05-21 07:53:10','<div class=\"content-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"content-main\">\r\n<div class=\"banner-nner\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-42\" src=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/careers-header.jpg\" alt=\"careers-header\" width=\"980\" height=\"200\" /></div>\r\n<div id=\"breadcrumbMenu\">\r\n<div class=\"breadcrumb\"><a href=\"http://103.230.84.14/\">Home</a><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-20\" src=\"http://103.230.84.14/wp-conte