12px;\">\r\n<div class=\"header-text-1\">About Us</div>\r\neCentric is Indian arm of the US$100 Million ParadigmIT Group. Established in 2002 as an RPO and offshore venture of ParadigmIT US, eCentric has subsequently built expertise in enterprise IT solutions and end to end human resource solutions.\r\n\r\neCentric is a CMMi Level 3, ISO 9001, ISO 27001 certified company with proven delivery capabilities in software development, support services, Recruitment Process Outsourcing, Business Process Outsourcing and end-to-end human resource solutions. We currently work with Fortune 500 companies and organizations from Government of India, US Government and large and medium Indian corporates.\r\n</div>\r\n[contact_form]\r\n</div>','About Us','','inherit','open','open','','18-revision-v1','','','2014-06-10 07:51:03','2014-06-10 07:51:03','',18,'http://ecentrichr.com/18-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(787,1,'2014-06-10 07:52:12','2014-06-10 07:52:12','<div class=\"body-block\">\r\n<div class=\"contentt-block\" style=\"margin-top: 12px;\">\r\n<div class=\"header-text-1\">Company Overview</div>\r\n<h1 class=\"content-text-1\">eCENTRIC</h1>\r\neCentric is Indian arm of the US$100 Million ParadigmIT Group. Established in 2002 as an RPO and offshore venture of ParadigmIT US, eCentric has subsequently built expertise in enterprise IT solutions and end to end human resource solutions.\r\n\r\neCentric is a CMMi Level 3, ISO 9001, ISO 27001 certified company with proven delivery capabilities in software development, support services, Recruitment Process Outsourcing, Business Process Outsourcing and end-to-end human resource solutions. We currently work with Fortune 500 companies and organizations from Government of India, US Government and large and medium Indian corporates.\r\n<h1 class=\"content-text-1\">eCentricHR</h1>\r\nWith over 16 years of experience in this field eCentricHR is the human resource solutions business of the company and focusses on providing search, selection, staffing, staff augmentation and training in India and USA. At eCentric we believe in providing customers with efficient and <b class=\"testimonials\">effective human resource solutions</b> on back of proprietary delivery process and mechanism.\r\n\r\nOur focus on offering efficient and timely solutions to customer has allowed us to deploy over 2500 resources across India in short span of last 3 years. We continue to deliver top tier talent across industry verticals and solutions with dedicated team based out of all major Indian cities and USA.\r\n\r\neCentricHR is member of industry bodies such as Indian Staffing Federation (ISF) , Associated Chambers of Commerce and Industry of India (ASSOCHAM), National Association of Software and Services Companies (NASSCOM) and TiE.\r\n</div>\r\n[contact_form]\r\n</div>','Company Overview','','inherit','open','open','','116-revision-v1','','','2014-06-10 07:52:12','2014-06-10 07:52:12','',116,'http://ecentrichr.com/116-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(788,1,'2014-06-10 07:55:41','2014-06-10 07:55:41','<div class=\"body-block\">\r\n<div class=\"contentt-block\" style=\"margin-top:12px;\">\r\n<div class=\"header-text-1\">Vision</div>\r\nProvide comprehensive and careful recruiting, screening, hiring and training services enabling both client and associates to achieve their business and personal goals.\r\n\r\nFulfill commitment to our clients and associates and be both their human resource and growth partner.\r\n\r\nTo be the best human capital and other professional solutions provider to Indian and Global industries based on process driven delivery systems\r\n<div class=\"header-text-1\">Mission</div>\r\nTo be a global scale efficient end to end human resources solutions company delivering value to our clients and associates.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[contact_form]\r\n</div>','Vision & Mission','','inherit','open','open','','141-revision-v1','','','2014-06-10 07:55:41','2014-06-10 07:55:41','',141,'http://ecentrichr.com/141-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(789,1,'2014-06-10 07:55:51','2014-06-10 07:55:51','<div class=\"body-block\">\r\n<div class=\"contentt-block\" style=\"margin-top: 12px;\">\r\n<div class=\"header-text-1\">Value Proposition</div>\r\nWe are a process driven organization with a core value of ‘customer first’. We focus on delivering HR solutions that bring value and innovation to our customers, our ability to integrate people, process and technology comes from our core values of\r\n<ul> \r\n<li>Customer first</li>\r\n<li>Process adherence </li>\r\n<li>Technology</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n[contact_form]\r\n</div>','Value Proposition','','inherit','open','open','','147-revision-v1','','','2014-06-10 07:55:51','2014-06-10 07:55:51','',147,'http://ecentrichr.com/147-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(790,1,'2014-06-10 07:56:03','2014-06-10 07:56:03','<div class=\"body-block\">\r\n<div class=\"contentt-block\" style=\"margin-top:12px;\">\r\n<div class=\"header-text-1\">Leadership</div>\r\n<div class=\"content-text-1\">Sridhar Gadhi: Founder and Group CEO</div>\r\nSridhar is a first generation entrepreneur. He started Paradigm InfoTech in 1998, eCentric Solutions in 2002 and has been growing the group ever since. He is a dynamic leader and built companies by developing leaders and successful teams. He has abilities to build companies in various industries that have huge growth prospects and steer them to success. Sridhar was awarded Entrepreneur of the year award by Ernst &amp;Young and Young Entrepreneurs Award by TANA. Prior to starting Paradigm InfoTech, he worked with IBM and Satyam Computers. He holds a degree in Master’s of Science in Computers and is a graduate from the Harvard Business School. He is an active member of Young Presidents Organisation, a Charter Member of TiE Hyderabad and is on the governing council of AP Society for Knowledge Networks and also on the academic council of Vignan University.\r\n<div class=\"content-text-1\">Karthik Krishnan: Chief Financial Officer &amp; CEO – eCentricHR:</div>\r\nKarthik brings with him 14 years of experience of working with large corporate houses in Business strategy, corporate finance and Business Intelligence. Prior to Paradigm, he worked in leadership roles with A F Ferguson &amp; Co. (Deloitte), Chartered Accountants, Arvind Mills, Maini Precision Components and NSL Group. He is a qualified Chartered Accountant with proven track record in managing large scale enterprises.\r\n<div class=\"content-text-1\">Arindam Chakraborthy: Senior Vice President – IT Staffing</div>\r\nArindam is an IT veteran with 26  years of experience and was instrumental  in essaying roles in Business & Change Management, Delivery & Sales Operations and P&L Management Pan India for different organizations. He joins us from Technosoft Global Corp. where he was responsible for setting up the business from the inception stage and scaling it to a world class Managed and Consulting Services Centre. Prior to this he has held various key leadership positions at Magna InfoTech, Ingram Micro, InfoTech Enterprises and other prominent enterprises. An MBA from Salt Lake Institute of Technical Training in Calcutta University, with Graduation in Commerce from St. Xavier’s College, Arindam is a certified Sales Specialist from HP/Compaq.\r\n<div class=\"content-text-1\">Siva Prasad Nanduri: Head of IT Staffing:</div>\r\nSiva brings to eCentric an experience of 17 years in sales, staff augmentation and staffing. Prior to eCentric Siva has served with TEK Systems, Adecco, Tata Teleservices TBA and GE iGate Capital. He is a qualified management graduate from IIM Kolkata and a qualified six sigma practioner.\r\n<div class=\"content-text-1\">Rob Studer: President</div>\r\nRob brings over 20 years of work experience. Rob has extensive experience in Wireless, Mobile Apps, Security and ERP. Strong customer relationships and rapid revenue growth under his leadership has been the driving force behind acquisitions of companies. Rob has also done business with companies such as Comcast, Time Warner, CableVision, Sprint and BrightHouse Networks. Rob is a graduate of the Iowa State University School of Business.\r\n<div class=\"content-text-1\">Chrishtopher Ponsford: Vice President</div>\r\nChris has over 17 years of experience in rail transportation, medical, electronics and aerospace. He has designed and implemented Quality Standards procedures interfacing directly with customers and development teams globally creating successful profitable solutions for fortune 500 companies globally. By understanding their needs, Chris creates innovative solutions to fit customers goals and budgets.</div>\r\n[contact_form]\r\n</div>\r\n','Leadership','','inherit','open','open','','153-revision-v1','','','2014-06-10 07:56:03','2014-06-10 07:56:03','',153,'http://ecentrichr.com/153-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(791,1,'2014-06-10 07:56:26','2014-06-10 07:56:26','<div class=\"body-block\">\r\n<div class=\"contentt-block\" style=\"margin-top:12px;\">\r\n<div class=\"header-text-1\" style=\"padding: 0 0 10px 0;\">Services</div>\r\n<div class=\"services-css\">\r\n<div class=\"services-css-1\">\r\n<div class=\"services-css-img\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-58\" style=\"border: 1px #CCCCCC solid; border-radius: 5px;\" src=\"http://ecentrichr.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/icon-2.png\" alt=\"icon-2\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"services-css-text\"><a href=\"http://ecentrichr.com/services/it-talent-management/\">IT Talent Management</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"services-css-2\">\r\n<div class=\"services-css-img\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-59\" style=\"border: 1px #CCCCCC solid; border-radius: 5px;\" src=\"http://ecentrichr.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/icon-3.png\" alt=\"icon-3\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"services-css-text\"><a href=\"http://ecentrichr.com/services/permanent-recruitment/\">Permanent Recruitment</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"services-css\">\r\n<div class=\"s